<paragraph id="0981FC20AA48D10A1367CD4D30E7BCD2" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">BMNH 1907.2.1.5a, two slides from type, R.N. 167, Gulf of Mannaar, Sri Lanka.</paragraph>
